\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" style=\"stroke: black;\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <circle cx=\"300\" cy=\"170\" r=\"148\" transform=\"scale(-1 1) translate(-600 0)  rotate(180 300 170)\"></circle> <line class=\"radius-line\" x1=\"300\" y1=\"169\" x2=\"448\" y2=\"169\"></line>  <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"360\" y=\"158\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">1</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"350\" y=\"185\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">sec θ</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"350\" y=\"205\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">cos θ</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"282\" y=\"187\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">O</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"282\" y=\"9\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">y</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"450\" y=\"168\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">P</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"425\" y=\"187\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">Q</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"520\" y=\"190\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">x</text></svg></div></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 5</b>: Círculo con radio 1 que contiene triángulos y algunas funciones trigonométricas expuestas.</p>",
               "source": [],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "En el momento en que el radio comienza a girar, el coseno de theta (θ) comenzará a reducir su valor, dirigiéndose hacia cero. Como consecuencia de esto, la secante comenzará a crecer indefinidamente. De esta forma, el **Gráfico 5**, en el límite cuando el coseno se aproxima a cero, quedaría como:",
               "source": [],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p id=\"circtri4\"><style>.circle-draw circle, .circle-draw line {stroke: #71a6d2; stroke-width: 4; stroke-linecap: round; fill: none;} .circle-draw circle { stroke-dasharray: 942; stroke-dashoffset: 942; animation: drawCircle 2s linear forwards;} .radius-line { transform-origin: 300px 170px; animation: rotateRadius 2s linear forwards;} .radius-45 { opacity: 0; animation: showRadius45 0.3s ease-out forwards; animation-delay: 2s; } .radius-30{ opacity: 0; animation: showRadius30 0.3s ease-out forwards; animation-delay: 2s; } .vertical45 { opacity: 0; animation: showVertical45 0.3s ease-out forwards; animation-delay: 2.5s; } .atlasTextRadius { opacity: 0; animation: atlasTextRadiusMov 0.3s ease-out forwards; animation-delay: 2.8s; }</style><style>@keyframes drawCircle { to {stroke-dashoffset: 0; } } @keyframes rotateRadius { from { transform: rotate(0deg); } to   { transform: rotate(-360deg); } } @keyframes showRadius45 { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } } @keyframes showRadius30 { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } } @keyframes showVertical45 { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }  @keyframes atlasTextRadiusMov { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }</style><div class=\"atlasCircleContainer\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 600 340\" class=\"circle-draw\" id=\"svgcirctri0\">  <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"3\" markerHeight=\"3\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" /></marker> </defs> <line x1=\"300\" y1=\"169\" x2=\"520\" y2=\"169\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" style=\"stroke: black;\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <line x1=\"300\" y1=\"169\" x2=\"300\" y2=\"8\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" style=\"stroke: black;\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <line x1=\"300\" y1=\"169\" x2=\"130\" y2=\"169\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" style=\"stroke: black;\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <line x1=\"300\" y1=\"169\" x2=\"300\" y2=\"330\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" style=\"stroke: black;\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <circle cx=\"300\" cy=\"170\" r=\"148\" transform=\"scale(-1 1) translate(-600 0)  rotate(180 300 170)\"></circle>  <line class=\"radius-line\" x1=\"300\" y1=\"169\" x2=\"338\" y2=\"29\"></line> <line class=\"radius-line\" x1=\"300\" y1=\"169\" x2=\"868\" y2=\"169\"></line>  <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"360\" y=\"158\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">1</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"325\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">cos θ</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"282\" y=\"187\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">O</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"282\" y=\"9\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">y</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"450\" y=\"168\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">P</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"425\" y=\"187\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">Q</text> <text class=\"atlasTextRadius\" x=\"520\" y=\"190\" font-size=\"1.3em\" font-weight=\"bold\">x</text></svg></div></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Gráfico 6</b>: Círculo con radio 1 que contiene triángulos y algunas funciones trigonométricas expuestas.</p>",
               "source": [],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "En este último gráfico, mantuvimos el coseno de theta (θ) visible, pero la secante se ha expandido de tal manera que su texto ya no es visible.\n\n#### Conclusión\n\nA pesar de ser poco utilizada (<htcite0>), no se puede negar la existencia de esta función, motivo por el cual exploramos, en este texto, sus gráficos para reforzar el conocimiento que estamos construyendo.",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "603c44f8-9b51-44f3-a538-9ddc6ba7be05",
                     "text": "Weisstein, Eric W.",
                     "page": "Secante",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  }
               ],
